asset.hookText:
Being on trend requires creativity, today’s look is a modern take on the classic side bun. It's effortlessly chic. 

How to get a Messy Side Bun with Style&Go collection: 

Step 1 
Split the front of your hair and fix your hair with a clip. Then pull the top of the hair into a low side ponytail and secure with a clear elastic. Fasten the bottom of the hair into a second ponytail and position right below the first.
Split. 

Step 2 
Finger comb the ends together to create one main ponytail and backcomb it to add dramatic volume to your hair! 

Step 3
Wrap the hair around the base, fix your hair with bobby pins and tease as desired.

Step 4
Curl one strand in the front using your mini straightener.
